{"tid":1652184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人加油！","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:04:11.000Z","uid":322311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"211625cc168fdc02c7ba78779624be1867ba004d","tid":1652184,"uid":322311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"不知不覺已經四個幾月<br />\n返工返學可能已經係每一日最放鬆嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇新聞嘅時候，都好傷心好憤怒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府從來都無聆聽過我哋嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每一日，都覺得好疲累。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港，幾時可以真係一個屬於香港人嘅地方？</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要堅持落去。<br />\n有嘢屈住喺心到唔開心，一定一定要同身邊嘅人訴苦！<br />\n<br />\n我相信我哋最後可以喺煲底下相聚。<br />\n我哋一定會贏！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人反抗！加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a61e16122e3ce376a5a25a13a1f9fbe1a4f0f1a0","tid":1652184,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1be54530891087f27a791e875c43b097f29a0a42","tid":1652184,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"push"}]}